&lt;li&gt;A domain name pointed to your cluster&amp;rsquo;s ingress controller (we&amp;rsquo;ll use &lt;code&gt;go.example.com&lt;/code&gt; in this guide)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
